    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036260/extras/df8f4e97afd71cef032f0c0b3e5c82e8.avif?t=1765310915\" width=599 height=100 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>穿越时空的冒险</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Wylde Society》的故事发生在世纪之交的繁华小镇费尔黑文。你可在此探索受近代启发的时尚、建筑、社会规则及礼仪。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>经营自己的魔法寄宿公寓</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >翻新和扩建怀尔德家庭寄宿公寓！邀请租户，让他们在入住期间感到宾至如归。有些客人只会住一季，但在你的帮助下，其他人可能会找到永远留下来的理由。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036260/extras/eedf4264d2ffd8d16cc134ab7fb58ced.poster.avif?t=1765310915\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036260/extras/eedf4264d2ffd8d16cc134ab7fb58ced.webm?t=1765310915\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036260/extras/eedf4264d2ffd8d16cc134ab7fb58ced.mp4?t=1765310915\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>举办精彩派对</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为一名大巫师社交名流，你将计划并举办一系列精彩的社交活动，包括茶会、晚宴和舞会，还将选择宾客名单、菜单、座位安排等事宜。你会引发一场戏剧性事件……还是激起一段浪漫情缘？</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>探索彼岸</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >曾几何时，降灵会可是项流行活动，但要分辨真正的灵媒和骗子可不容易！薇薇安确实有联系灵界的天赋。你会帮助谁的灵魂完成他们未竟之事？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036260/extras/e7b3087d0f54470adfc4e4ff055441b6.poster.avif?t=1765310915\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036260/extras/e7b3087d0f54470adfc4e4ff055441b6.webm?t=1765310915\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036260/extras/e7b3087d0f54470adfc4e4ff055441b6.mp4?t=1765310915\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>结交魔法生物</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >发现并收集从猫到水獭的迷人妖精。这些友好的伙伴具有独特的魔法天赋，还很喜欢陪伴你（甚至骑在你的扫帚上）！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i>更多新功能消息即将公布！</i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036260/extras/68e1c8833ed8a4c761b8bc635db8bf22.poster.avif?t=1765310915\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036260/extras/68e1c8833ed8a4c761b8bc635db8bf22.webm?t=1765310915\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036260/extras/68e1c8833ed8a4c761b8bc635db8bf22.mp4?t=1765310915\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
